data.description: Welcome to your new home! This beautiful, meticulously maintained, semi-detached rambler-style home is perfect for those looking for the ease of main level living! As soon as you walk in the front door you are enveloped in natural light from the floor to ceiling windows illuminating the open living/dining space. These rooms are adorned with crown molding and feature new luxury vinyl plank flooring all the way back through the kitchen. The kitchen has been upgraded with new countertops, updated wide plank flooring, and lovely tile backsplash. From the kitchen you can step into the showstopping backyard, the best in the community! The large, green lot is surrounded by a 6 foot privacy fence which converts to an idyllic white picket fence framing the front yard. Talk about curb appeal! Back inside you will find three bedrooms, all with crown molding and vinyl flooring, as well as a charming, updated full bathroom. For extra storage, there is an attic that can absolutely be used as such, as well as two rear storage sheds! Move into this home with peace of mind knowing your major systems are updated. The HVAC is 4 years old, the roof was replaced 9 years ago and has two sets of solar panels that maximize your green energy potential and basically zero out your electric bill, or pay you at times, and the windows and doors have been replaced as well. A fantastic home in a wonderful location, come schedule your tour today! ** Accepting Back up Offers**
